Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:24.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,These words lured men to the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:26.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they'd ever dared to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:29.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is the time known as the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:33.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come aboard and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:35.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,bring along all your hopes and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:41.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Together we will find everything that we're looking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:41.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:42.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:53.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The compass left behind It'll only slow us down Your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,heart will be your guide Raise the sails and take the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:04.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,helm That legendary place That the end of the map
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:09.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,reveals Is only legendary until someone proves it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:10.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,real.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:14.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Through it all, through all the troubled times,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:18.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,through the heartache and through the pain, know that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:21.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I will be there to stand by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just like I know you'll stand by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:28.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So come aboard and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:31.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,bring along all your hopes and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:35.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Together we will find everything that we're looking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:35.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,for.
