Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.01,0:01:56.26,Title-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(726,728)\3c&H1E1E1E&\c&H1E1E1E&\bord2.3\1a&HFF&\t(684,726,\1a&H00&)\t(5522,5564,\1a&HFF&)}Captain Kuro
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.01,0:01:56.26,Title-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(726,728)\c&HE7E6E6&\bord0\4a&HFF&}Captain Kuro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't call it murder, Django.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:55.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't like the sound of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:58.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:02:00.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's an accident that you planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:04.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uh, what are those guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:05.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maybe if we listen a little closer, we can find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We can't simply kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It is critical to our plan that Miss Kaya perishes in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,an unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:16.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So don't screw that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:20.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So basically, on your signal, the men and I stormed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,the village and managed to accidentally kill the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,little rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Then you get her inheritance and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,we all get paid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:28.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Your ignorance is astounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're not related,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,so how could I inherit anything from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You'll work very hard to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:37.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, Django, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is the most important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:43.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Before you kill her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,you'll use your hypnosis to make Kaia write her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:49.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And it will say I leave my entire fortune to my
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,butler, Klawhador.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:56.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Then and only then will I have undisputed control of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,her enormous fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And no one will suspect a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I have spent three long years gaining the trust of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,everyone around me so that it would be unsurprising
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:10.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,for her to leave the entirety of her inheritance to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:10.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Three years as a butler for this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:18.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You sure had us scared back then, Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:22.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, you suddenly said you were giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,life as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,In no time at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,you set up someone to be your double.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Then you let the world see Captain Kuro get executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Only now do I understand that was just the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:44.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,of this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You are the man of a thousand plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Never call me that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I abandoned that name years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I now wish to obtain my wealth without attracting the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,attention of the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,In other words, I'm a pacifist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The pacifist you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:07.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Murdering an entire family\Ndoesn't exactly qualify as peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I haven't murdered an entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The father's death wasn't planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, it makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If it's all the same to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,hurry up and give the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The crew is getting bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:24.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting in the\Nwaters near here for over a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:30.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And the men are growing more anxious by the minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:34.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is really horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is it bad guy stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:43.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening to any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:47.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Those guys aren't just bad, they're evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro is known to be the most devious,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,scheming pirate around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And though he's known for his smarts,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,he's legendary for his brutality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Word had it that the Marines caught and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,executed him three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But Captain Kuro is alive and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,well, posing as Klawhador the butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And he's had his diabolical sights set on Kaya's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,fortune for the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,First they'll attack the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,then they'll kill Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:26.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:27.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They'll see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You better stay away from that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You idiot, they've spotted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:37.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,hide before they decide you need a long, slow death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,if it isn't Usopp, the mischievous town liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm spotted, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Did you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:53.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We didn't hear a peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We just got here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,so we didn't hear anything about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We heard it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:57.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:05.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:09.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pay attention, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And watch this ring closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:12.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:13.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's some kind of weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:21.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,By the count of Django, you will be in a deep sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:22.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,One... Run for cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:24.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's going to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Django!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:32.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Django, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I see you're still falling asleep on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:47.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He had to go and fall off a cliff, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A pity, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But there's no way he could have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:56.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's really dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What about the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Shall I take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Everything he could say would sound like lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:12.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Django, tomorrow at daybreak\Nthe men are to attack the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rough up the villagers some and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,tear up their homes a little for good measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And above all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:20.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,make sure Miss Kaya's death looks accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:22.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just accept it, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There is nothing you can say or
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:30.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,do to warn the villagers of this impending tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,My plans are flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:47.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:52.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the village I grew up with is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And Kaya's going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:58.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm Usopp, brave warrior of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I heard you've been a little down lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd tell you a story to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You would do well to mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:10.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please leave or
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll call someone who will make you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:16.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:19.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I fought, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Noooooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I thought Luffy was supposed to be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is he still at the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wow, he looked really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:49.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:50.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Still mad at the butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:53.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't just a mad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That look was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:01.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It was a tragic face of sheer desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:04.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you guys show us the way to get down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:04.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,to that shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This smells like an adventure to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something happened at the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I think this calls for the Usopp Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How do we get to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Terrible news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:23.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Everybody run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:26.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Everybody run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:26.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning they're going to attack the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All right, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're putting a stop to this here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:00.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:01.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's the truth this time, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We all know that you're nothing but a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It would do you some good to follow Klawhador's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,example of hard work and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Everything he could say would sound like lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:19.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is exactly what Klawhador is counting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He ignored me because
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,he knew no one would believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are these to your liking, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Custom made to your exact specifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It was quite a trip to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:47.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for\Ntraveling so far to get them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're a gift, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:55.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As of tomorrow, it will be exactly three years to the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,day since Klawhador arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's always taken such good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He'll be delighted to receive such a lovely gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please hear me out, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:12.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Our lives depend on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:13.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:15.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pirates are going to attack\Nthe village in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:18.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If we believed every story you ever told us, we would
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,have run screaming from the\Nvillage hundreds of times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:21.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying this time, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:27.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:29.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They'll murder you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You'll be lucky if we don't murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,After three long years of absence,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:53.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I made the call for my men, and you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Your loyalty will be richly rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I intend on being more than generous when
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I divide the take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,At dawn tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,destroy the village to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If the pirates are going to attack the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,then they're going to kill Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:22.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So, what made you think\Nit'd be a good time for a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't remember going to sleep or
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,getting down here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:35.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This proves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klawhador is a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp saw right through him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I bet he's on his way to warn the villagers so
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,they'll have time to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Those stupid pirates won't hurt anyone because the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,town will be abandoned by the time they get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:49.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We'd better run away too if we want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All right, let's pack our\Ntreasure and run like the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:58.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We need to stock up before the meat shop guy leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come on, that's not really the issue at hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:24.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:32.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:35.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I was worried you wouldn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:36.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:37.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Run, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Someone's going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's tricked the entire village!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klawhador's really a deadly pirate captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is this a story?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This isn't one of my stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I heard it with my own ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klawhador is a pirate captain who weaseled his way into
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,your family's home so he could steal your fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's pretended to be your butler for three years so
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,he could kill you and inherit your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,His crew is going to raid the village at dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and in the process, you're going to get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klawhador's a very bad man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Your life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You have to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I did treat you harshly earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and I understand that you're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:34.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But lying like this, it's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I loved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All those lies you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They brought joy to my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,but this is just vengeful poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya, please, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm not just trying to get back at Klawhador.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:02.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:05.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:10.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya, is everything okay up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Unhand her immediately, you villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please trust me, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You gotta get out of this village\Nbefore that butler gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:45.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C'mon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I promise this'll all make sense tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,but right now we need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya, please, please, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Leave Miss Kai alone, you maniac!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't let that lunatic get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:42.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He broke in and tried to\Nkidnap the lady of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why won't anyone believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There, there, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Everything's going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, how's it going, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:40.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're alive again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:41.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I had a pretty good nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He was sleeping the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:48.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain, we heard all about\Nthose pirates and their evil plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We better hurry and warn the people in the village so
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:52.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,they have time to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:53.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Warn the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:01.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We all know you're nothing but a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:14.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously I'm lying like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That butler made me so mad with what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:18.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd get him back and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,say that he was a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You put the Straw Hat guy up to it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you've really disappointed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:36.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:39.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Even though that butler guy is a jerk, I thought you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,were better than lying to hurt someone and I admired
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,you for being such a kind-hearted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And to think, we respected you this entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's supper time anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So, how come you lied to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Because all I do is lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:05.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's no way anybody was\Ngoing to believe what I had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:06.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why should they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Because what you were\Ntelling them was the honest truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:12.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They are coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and they're going to level this whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They'll think I'm lying if I try to warn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the village thinks that tomorrow's just
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,going to be another normal day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They think I'm lying and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,that's all they need to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop those pirates\Nat the beach tomorrow myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault for being such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore if they drive me away with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,brooms or shoot me in the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:41.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:45.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's my home and I love everyone in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:50.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I have to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're a hell of a good guy, sending your cronies
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:56.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,away and going into battle alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I have dibs on all the pirate treasure, you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So you want a little help or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:02.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're going to help me fight all these pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:09.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, you said there's a\Nwhole bunch of bad guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:11.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And you look scared out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,For your information, I have nerves of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly okay with tons of bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:19.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,After all, you're looking at the legendary Captain Usopp, 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,brave warrior of the high seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All right, fine, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're Captain Kuro's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,These guys mean business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't need pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If you guys are sticking around because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,you pity me, just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:37.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't need you laughing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're not laughing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're helping because you are honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You really think we'd risk our lives out of pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You guys!
